      <title>马克龙和舒尔茨承诺将资本市场谈判变为现实</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/macron-scholz-pledge-to-turn-capital-markets-talk-into-reality</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙表示，经过多年讨论，德国和法国已同意迅速推进深化欧盟资本市场，以促进对欧盟的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/macron-scholz-pledge-to-turn-capital-markets-talk-into-reality</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 19:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰预算赤字料扩大，借款将增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/new-zealand-seen-posting-bigger-budget-deficits-borrowing-more</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管新西兰收入减少，但新政府仍坚持减税，因此其首份预算中赤字可能会扩大，借款也会增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/new-zealand-seen-posting-bigger-budget-deficits-borrowing-more</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>律师告诉封口费陪审员，特朗普是敲诈勒索的受害者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/trump-was-victim-of-extortion-lawyer-tells-hush-money-jurors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的封口费刑事审判律师向纽约陪审团辩称，这位前总统是敲诈勒索的受害者，并称此案的根源在于有人试图在 2016 年大选之前向他勒索钱财。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/trump-was-victim-of-extortion-lawyer-tells-hush-money-jurors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 18:06:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博茨瓦纳政府向马斯克的 Starlink 颁发运营许可证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/botswana-government-grants-musk-s-starlink-an-operating-license</link>
      <description><![CDATA[博茨瓦纳向 SpaceX 的 Starlink 部门颁发了许可证，这是最新一个允许这家互联网服务公司运营的非洲国家，此前该公司威胁要限制未经许可的地区的服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/botswana-government-grants-musk-s-starlink-an-operating-license</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 17:52:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受石油供应紧张影响，顶级保险公司将退出哥伦比亚公共系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/top-insurer-to-leave-colombia-s-public-system-amid-petro-squeeze</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚最大的健康保险公司之一将逐步停止在该国公共系统的运营，以避免其财务状况进一步恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/top-insurer-to-leave-colombia-s-public-system-amid-petro-squeeze</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 17:39:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈佛大学计划在争议问题上保持沉默</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/harvard-plans-to-stay-silent-on-controversial-issues-after-furor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈佛大学因哈马斯袭击以色列以及随后在加沙发动的报复性战争而陷入数月动荡，该校将不再就“不直接影响大学核心功能”的公共事务发表官方声明。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/harvard-plans-to-stay-silent-on-controversial-issues-after-furor</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 17:30:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙称基辅必须具备打击俄罗斯导弹基地的能力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/macron-says-ukraine-must-be-allowed-to-hit-russian-missile-sites</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙表示，必须允许乌克兰使用欧洲提供的武器瞄准俄罗斯境内的导弹机组人员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/macron-says-ukraine-must-be-allowed-to-hit-russian-missile-sites</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 17:14:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>格鲁吉亚议会推翻“外国代理人”法否决权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/georgian-parliament-overrides-veto-of-foreign-agent-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚立法者周二推翻了总统对有争议的“外国代理人”法的否决，无视美国和欧盟谴责的针对这项“受克里姆林宫启发”的措施的大规模抗议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/georgian-parliament-overrides-veto-of-foreign-agent-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 15:13:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟国家考虑允许乌克兰使用武器打击俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/eu-nations-discuss-easing-restrictions-on-weapons-sent-to-kyiv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟国防部长正在讨论是否允许乌克兰使用成员国运送的武器袭击俄罗斯境内深处的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/eu-nations-discuss-easing-restrictions-on-weapons-sent-to-kyiv</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 08:46:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
